            <text x="200" y="394" text-anchor="middle" fill="#3730A3" font-family="Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="11" font-weight="700" letter-spacing="0.15em" opacity="0.6">THE GRACE NETWORK</text>
